#CHIP YM2413
#CLOCK 3579545

; YM2413 (OPLL) Built-in Patches Test
;
; The YM2413 has 16 built-in patches (preset voices) plus a custom patch mode.
; This test validates the OPLL chip by playing notes across its 9 channels.
;
; Test sequence: Simple melody and harmony patterns

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; Channel 1: Melody
c4 . d4 . e4 .

r4

; Channel 2: Harmony
g4 . f4 . e4 .

r4

; Channel 3: Bass
c3 . . d3 . . e3 .

r4

; All 9 channels together (brief)
c4 & g4 & c3 .

r2

#END
